text: Irina Konstantinovna Khlebko (; born 30 November 1990) is a Russian female badminton player. == Achievements == === BWF Grand Prix === The BWF Grand Prix has two level such as Grand Prix and Grand Prix Gold. It is a series of badminton tournaments, sanctioned by Badminton World Federation (BWF) since 2007.
